    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what you're saying. about the memories and the lessons. but honestly, sometimes i look at them and i just think it would be so much kinder if i wasn't here to make them worry. like, wouldnt it be more selfless to just... make it easy for them so they can start their own lives without having to look back at me?",
